By now, we’re all familiar with the Waffle House Index.
For those of you who don’t understand: Waffle House is a glorious Southern institution that has spread to some areas outside the South.
If anyone is using the Waffle House Index to measure the coronavirus crisis, it may not quite be time to panic – depending on where you live.
Here’s to the amazing folks at Waffle House who are keeping the world going in a time of crisis.
Pray for them, and support Waffle House when you can.